Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh, girls! Don't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When I was a little filly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:08.53,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And the sun was going do-o-o-own
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:09.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Tell me she's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:11.22,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The darkness and the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:15.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,They would always make me fro-o-o-own
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:15.83,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:17.96,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'd hide under my pillow,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:20.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,From what I thought I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:22.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But Granny Pie said that wasn't the way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:24.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To deal with fears at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:25.46,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:28.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She said: "Pinkie you gotta stand up tall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Learn to face your fears
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll see, that they can't hurt you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:35.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Just laugh to make them disappear!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.92,0:00:37.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Ha! Ha! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.87,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So, giggle at the ghostly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.14,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Guffaw at the grossly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Crack up at the creepy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:49.68,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Whoop it up with the weepy-y-y
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.61,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Chortle at the kooky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:53.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Snortle at the spooky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.05,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And tell that big dumb scary face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:56.15,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To take a hike and leave you alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:57.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And if he thinks he can scare you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then he's got another thing coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:00:59.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,and the very idea of such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:00.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,just makes you wanna
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Laugh!